11 An act relating to legislative operations and government accountability
12 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
13 * * * Purpose and Findings * * *
14 Sec. 1. PURPOSE
15 (a) The purpose of this act is to actuate the principle of government
16 accountability by focusing on how evidence is used to inform policy, how our
17 State laws are carried out, and how legislation can best be formed to achieve its
18 intended outcomes. This act strives to systematize government accountability
19 efforts as much as possible with simple, clear, independent, objective, and fact-
